{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-quiz-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-quiz-describing-a-company/es-a1-quiz-describing-a-company","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Pokušao sam da opišem kompaniju","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ovaj test proverava vaše razumevanje glagola trećeg lica množine, strukture osnovnih rečenica i informacija o kompaniji na španski.</p>\n<p>Da bi položio test, moraš tačno odgovoriti na najmanje 9 od 10 pitanja koja su ispod.</p>\n</section>","challengeType":8,"helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","block":"es-a1-quiz-describing-a-company","fields":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/#es-a1-quiz-describing-a-company","slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-quiz-describing-a-company/es-a1-quiz-describing-a-company"},"quizzes":[{"questions":[{"distractors":["<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Andes Commerce tiene una empresa de tecnología.</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Andes Commerce está una empresa de tecnología.</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Andes Commerce se llama una empresa de tecnología.</span></p>"],"text":"<p>Koja od sledećih rečenica ima ispravan glagol?</p>","answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Andes Commerce es una empresa de tecnología.</span></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">La empresa llamo Andes Commerce.</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">La empresa llamar Andes Commerce.</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">La empresa llama Andes Commerce.</span></p>"],"text":"<p>Koja je rečenica koja pravilno koristi treće lice množine da spomene kompaniju?</p>","answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">La empresa se llama Andes Commerce.</span></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Es</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Está</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Se llama</span></p>"],"text":"<p>Koji je glagol koji znači <strong>\"ana\"</strong> za treće lice jednine?</p>","answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Tiene</span></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">La empresa tiene en Medellín.</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">La empresa se llama en Medellín.</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">La empresa es en Medellín.</span></p>"],"text":"<p>Koja rečenica tačno navodi lokaciju kompanije?</p>","answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">La empresa está en Medellín.</span></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Empresa es tecnología.</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Tiene la empresa setenta empleados.</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Es empresa tecnología.</span></p>"],"text":"<p>Koja rečenica prati pravilnu strukturu <strong>imenica + glagol trećeg lica</strong>?</p>","answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">La empresa es una empresa de tecnología.</span></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">La departamento de ingeniería tiene diez empleados.</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Ingeniería departamento tiene diez empleados.</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Departamento de ingeniería tiene diez empleados.</span></p>"],"text":"<p>Koja rečenica pravilno koristi priložje da opiše odeljenje?</p>","answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">El departamento de ingeniería tiene diez empleados.</span></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">es</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">está</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">se llama</span></p>"],"text":"<p>Koji glagol pravilno dovršava rečenicu?</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">La empresa ___ setenta y tres empleados.</span></p>","answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">tiene</span></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Su sitio web tiene www.andescommerce.com.</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">La empresa llama www.andescommerce.com.</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Está la empresa es www.andescommerce.com.</span></p>"],"text":"<p>Koja rečenica tačno identifikuje veb-sajt kompanije?</p>","answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Su sitio web es www.andescommerce.com.</span></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p>Kompanija radi u Andes Commerce.</p>","<p>Kompanija se nalazi u Andes Commerce.</p>","<p>Kompanija ima Andes Commerce.</p>"],"text":"<p>Koja je tačan prevod ove rečenice?</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">La empresa se llama Andes Commerce.</span></p>","answer":"<p>Kompanija se zove Andes Commerce.</p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p>Kompanija ima sedamdeset tri zaposlena.</p>","<p>Kompanija ima sedamdeset tri zaposlena.</p>","<p>Kompanija se zove sedamdeset tri zaposlenika.</p>"],"text":"<p>Koja rečenica tačno određuje koliko zaposlenih kompanija ima?</p>","answer":"<p>Preduzeće ima sedamdeset tri zaposlenika.</p>","audioData":null}]}],"tests":[],"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/#es-a1-quiz-describing-a-company","dashedName":"es-a1-quiz-describing-a-company","certification":"a1-professional-spanish","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","chapter":"es-a1-chapter-describing-company-and-people","module":"es-a1-module-describing-a-company","block":"es-a1-quiz-describing-a-company","isFirstStep":true,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-warm-up-describing-people-at-work-basics/task-1","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-review-talking-about-a-company/glossary","id":"696edf13152f88ef815b